@self (myself/himself/herself/themself/itself/etc. Follows a preposition such as about/etc.)@|@себе (pron: pc/reflexive - The word means self. It is used when the pronoun is the same person or thing as the subject and is translated as myself/himself/herself/etc. Follows a preposition such as о/обо/etc.)@
@self (myself/himself/herself/themself/itself/etc.)@|@себе (pron: dc/reflexive - The word means self. It is used when the pronoun is the same person or thing as the subject and is translated as myself/himself/herself/etc.), себой (pron: ic/reflexive - The word means self. It is used when the pronoun is the same person or thing as the subject and is translated as myself/himself/herself/etc.), себя (pron: ac/reflexive - The word means self. It is used when the pronoun is the same person or thing as the subject and is translated as myself/himself/herself/etc.), себя (pron: gc/reflexive - The word means self. It is used when the pronoun is the same person or thing as the subject and is translated as myself/himself/herself/etc.)@
